Take a pan and then add water. 
Add green chillies paste, baking soda, salt and boil it over medium flame.
Add rice flour.
Place it inside the steamer cover with the lead.
Steam cook for about ten minutes and turn off flame.
Open the lid and let it cool for few minutes.
Serve it with oil and red chily powder.ğŸ˜‹ğŸ˜‹
